item.description:
This is a listing from the York Public Library website that I thought some of us might be interested in. Isabeau (or Beau as I know her) is a medium I met through another club I belong to called the Seacoast Paranormal Research Group. I'll be there so if anyone wants to join me that would be a lot of fun!

Psychic and Psychological Perspectives on Intuition
Friday, November 14 7:00 p.m.
Isabeau Esby and Dr. Joel Glenn Wixson will offer various perspectives on the topics of self-empowerment, awareness, living naturally, reducing stress, trust and fear. (This program was originally presented on October 14). A question and answer session will follow.
item.name: Psychic and Psychological Perspectives on Intuition -- Presentation
